<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ ط ع:</span> <span class="c2">(أَهْطَعَ)</span> الرَّجُلُ إِذَا مَدَّ عُنُقَهُ وَصَوَّبَ رَأْسَهُ.<span class="c5"> وَأَهْطَعَ فِي عَدْوِهِ:</span> أَسْرَعَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>